<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #111;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            background: #6366f1;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .features {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .feature-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #6366f1;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://launchforge.app/logo-white.png" alt="LaunchForge" style="height: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px;" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
            <h1>Welcome to the Forge, <%= name %>!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>We're thrilled to have you here.</h2>
            <p>You've just taken the first step toward building a viral waitlist and growing your audience faster than ever before. LaunchForge was built to help founders like you launch with momentum.</p>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            <div class="features">
                <p style="margin-top:0; font-weight: 600; color: #111;">What's next?</p>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="feature-icon">✨</span>
                    Create your first viral waitlist in seconds.
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="feature-icon">📈</span>
                    Enable leaderboard and referral mechanics.
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🤖</span>
                    Get AI-powered growth insights for your workspace.
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions, just reply to this email. We're here to help!</p>
            <p>Best,<br>The LaunchForge Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 LaunchForge. All rights reserved.<br>
            You received this because you recently created a LaunchForge account.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
